snippet.title: Johnny Depp New Project Inspired By Amber Heard Split
snippet.description:
In today's video, we will be discussing Johnny Depp's new project Inspired by Amber heard split. 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
_______________________________________

JOHNNY DEPP, The Pirates of the Caribbean star was working on new material all last year during his split from Amber Heard and being let go from the Fantastic Beasts franchise, says close friend Alice Cooper: "He won't let any of that stop him." It's something Depp says he is very "proud of." 


Music In This Video : 

Track: Odessa — LiQWYD & Scandinavianz
